c60c5ffd-068a-5b91-ade5-0dbcf58e1b40,tg:rubgr:2350,e73_Descriptions,,id.desc,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,"[Blad 1, recto] Kh. Mus. [Wenen]. Jan Brueghel. Figure paintings: 63 Aeneas in Unterwelt: red fire probably on knowledge of Dulle Griet; 61 Kreuzigung - proportions of figures comparable to M. Van Cleve. Landsknechte (in yellow & red) like ?; inv. 667 Versuchung des Antonis very small (with red fire) very different from Washington; 60. Anbetung der Könige; 65. Der vornehme Besuch in der Bauern Stube (in colours); inv. 642 Rottenhammer & B. Ruhe auf der Flucht; 69. Versuchung Christi - see ? street; [Blad 1, verso] Inv. 815 Ceres &  4 Elements figures by H. van Balen; Inv. 814 Raub der Europa (figures by H. van Balen); 68 Dorf am Fluß; 71 Ein Überfall, figures by S. Vrancx; Pure landscpae inv. 1072 Waldlandschaft; Flower pieces: 74. Großer Blumenstrauß; 72 Kleiner Blumenstrauß; 73 Blumenstrauß in einer Vase; Animal studies: monkeys & donkeys; Inv. 6985 Tierstudie (ex Hunde); Inv. 6988 Tierstudie (ex Hunde) dogs; [blad 2, recto] Jan Brueghel 69. Versuchung Christi Tree barks painted in various ways - always very painterly but different from P.B. only the trunk of a birch lying on the brook shows parallel curves comparable to P.B. I. but in P.B. everything is broader not 'Feinmalerei'.",descriptive note,Nederlands,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,

column4: <content>[Blad 1, recto] Kh. Mus. [Wenen]. Jan Brueghel. Figure paintings: 63 Aeneas in Unterwelt: red fire probably on knowledge of Dulle Griet; 61 Kreuzigung - proportions of figures comparable to M. Van Cleve. Landsknechte (in yellow & red) like ?; inv. 667 Versuchung des Antonis very small (with red fire) very different from Washington; 60. Anbetung der Könige; 65. Der vornehme Besuch in der Bauern Stube (in colours); inv. 642 Rottenhammer & B. Ruhe auf der Flucht; 69. Versuchung Christi - see ? street; [Blad 1, verso] Inv. 815 Ceres &  4 Elements figures by H. van Balen; Inv. 814 Raub der Europa (figures by H. van Balen); 68 Dorf am Fluß; 71 Ein Überfall, figures by S. Vrancx; Pure landscpae inv. 1072 Waldlandschaft; Flower pieces: 74. Großer Blumenstrauß; 72 Kleiner Blumenstrauß; 73 Blumenstrauß in einer Vase; Animal studies: monkeys & donkeys; Inv. 6985 Tierstudie (ex Hunde); Inv. 6988 Tierstudie (ex Hunde) dogs; [blad 2, recto] Jan Brueghel 69. Versuchung Christi Tree barks painted in various ways - always very painterly but different from P.B. only the trunk of a birch lying on the brook shows parallel curves comparable to P.B. I. but in P.B. everything is broader not 'Feinmalerei'.</content>
